ActDepartment of Agriculture and Agri-Food Act
PrecisAuthority is requested for the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food for the purposes of providing funding to Provincial and/or Territorial governments for programs, initiatives and activities to support practices not traditionally associated with agriculture, and to enter into agreements with the government of a Province or Territory or any other organization, including contribution agreements, to implement these types of activities under the cost-shared component of Growing Forward.
